Newcastle fans are planning to boycott the club's next home game against Tottenham on April 19 . 
  A social media campaign has been launched in a bid to turn up the heat on owner Mike Ashley . 
  Newcastle fans will be encouraged to take part in demos before and after the game . 
  The Magpies face Tottenham at St James' Park on Sunday . 
  The game will be shown live on Sky Sports . 
 